"     Nicholas Vogelzang, MD",
"    </a>",
"    <br/>",
"    <a class=\"contributor contributor_credentials\" href=\"mobipreview.htm?37/39/38520/contributors\">",
"     W Robert Lee, MD, MS, MEd",
"    </a>",
"    <br/>",
"    <a class=\"contributor contributor_credentials\" href=\"mobipreview.htm?37/39/38520/contributors\">",
"     Jerome P Richie, MD, FACS",
"    </a>",
"    <br/>",
"   </div>",
